      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to stp-srt-inp-800.
       stp-srt-inp-120.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura sequenziale record [mgi]            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/iofmgi"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
