      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-ivp-ann-ivp       not  = rr-ann-dic or
                     rf-ivp-mes-ivp       >    rr-mes-fin
                     go to stp-srt-inp-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
