                     go to prn-fin-cic-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Stampa fincatura per dettaglio              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   stp-fnc-det-000      thru stp-fnc-det-999        .
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-fin-cic-999.
