                     add   1              to   w-stp-lgd-civ-nme
                     move  01             to   w-stp-lgd-civ-ele
                                              (w-stp-lgd-civ-nme)     .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se presenza aliquota non deducibile         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
