      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tai-snx-asi        =    "S"
                     add   1              to   w-stp-lgd-civ-nme
                     move  03             to   w-stp-lgd-civ-ele
                                              (w-stp-lgd-civ-nme)     .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
